          <div class="callout-label">⚡ TL;DR — Pick by your automation depth</div>
          <p><strong>You want drafts to edit:</strong> Jasper ($49) or Writesonic ($16). <strong>You want bulk output you publish:</strong> Byword ($99) or Autoblogging.ai ($49). <strong>You want articles live without touching anything:</strong> theStacc ($99/mo, full pipeline, auto-published).</p>
        </div>

        <div class="inline-cta">
          <div class="cta-copy">
            <h4>Don't want to brief, edit, or publish — just want articles live?</h4>
            <p>theStacc handles research, briefs, writing, optimisation, and publishing to WordPress / Webflow / Ghost. <strong>Content SEO module starts at $99/mo</strong> — no tool stack to learn.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cta-action">
            <a href="/demo/" class="cta-btn-inline">See a live demo <span>→</span></a>
            <span class="cta-meta">No card · 15-min walkthrough</span>
          </div>
        </div>

